---
title: Roasted Cauliflower and Falafel Plate with Garlicky Roasted Red Pepper Hummus
description: Golden, harissa-spiced cauliflower is coupled with crispy falafels in this Middle Eastern-inspired plate. Roasted red peppers add a delicious sweet quality to the hummus, which provides a creamy backdrop to all those earthy flavours!
